        <inline name="agenda item name">Administrative and budgetary aspects of the financing of the United Nations peacekeeping operations</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 29 June 2022</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#fifthCommittee">[on the report of the Fifth Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/76/874, para. 21</inline>)]</docProponent>
